package.name: UNL_Peoplefinder
package.summary: The UNL faculty staff and student directory.
package.description: The UNL_Peoplefinder package contains all the source code for the UNL directory. Additionally, this package provides an API which developers can use to retrieve directory information and perform searches.
package.notes:
Package UNL_Peoplefinder release notes for version 0.1.0.
Basic functionality is available. The default driver uses the web service, and no LDAP connection info is required.
